        "localization": {
          "name": "Restore Link",
          "description": "Grants Rizette's Link to another random non-conjured ally that does not already have a Link.\n\nThen that ally and the user:\n- are healed for 100% max HP.\n- have the TU costs for all of their skills reduced by 30%. This will overwrite the effects of other Quicken skills.\n- are granted a Sleep Ward, Stun Ward, Poison Ward and Instant Death Ward.\n\nUsable only if no other ally on the battlefield has Rizette's Link already, and there is a valid target. Usable 3 times per battle.\n\nEach Ward prevents their named effect from being applied once, then is removed. An Instant Death Ward prevents this unit from being immediately defeated without damage by a non-boss enemy once, then is removed. Instant Death Wards cannot be ignored. Identical Wards cannot stack.",
          "selected": "Give another ally Rizette's Link"
        }
      },
